The external sqlite-vec docs are narrowing this down: mixed float+bit columns, metadata limits, and SQL-side `vec_quantize_binary()` all check out. The risky area is D4, because sqlite-vec’s own release history shows `ALTER TABLE RENAME` support arriving after the pinned `0.1.7`, which puts the proposed rebuild/rename migration shape in question.
