   235	NOT NULL enforcement:
   236	
   237	- `embedding`, `embedding_bin`, `source_type`, `kind`,
   238	  `created_at` are all written on every insert by Pack 1's
   239	  writer; no row can land with a NULL.
   240	- vec0 metadata columns do not have a declarative `NOT NULL`
   241	  constraint in the sqlite-vec syntax shown in
